<span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Qi_Seasoning&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5.2\" title=\"Version History\">1.5.2</a>: Speed buffs can no longer be increased with Qi Seasoning. Buff durations from seasoned food/drink are now 50% longer.</li></ul>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414001958\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.098 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.110 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2198/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 13796/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 992/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 376/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.003/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 519 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   53.606      1 -total\n 54.43%   29.180      1 Template:Infobox\n 32.89%   17.629      1 Template:Description\n 22.14%   11.870      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 17.15%    9.194      1 Template:Name\n  5.58%    2.989      2 Template:History\n  4.28%    2.297      3 Template:Price\n  2.93%    1.570      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  2.86%    1.532      2 Template:Version\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:11934-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414001957 and revision id 190557\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Qi Seasoning\n|source      = [[Qi's Walnut Room]] for {{Price|10|gem}}\n|sellprice   = 200\n|quality     = false\n}}\n\n'''Qi Seasoning''' can be purchased from [[Qi's Walnut Room]] once unlocked.  The price is 10 Qi Seasoning for 10 {{Name|Qi Gem|class=inline}}s.\n\nHaving Qi Seasoning in the [[Inventory]], the refrigerator, or a [[Mini-Fridge]] will cause any dishes that the player [[cooking|cooks]] to become gold quality. The Qi Seasoning will be consumed on use.\n\nGold quality cooked dishes sell for 50% more than their normal quality counterparts, and recover 80% more health and energy when consumed. Gold quality dishes also give better buffs when eaten, adding +1 to the stats (excluding [[Speed]] buffs). The duration of the buffs are also increased by 50%.\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|hate=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Leo,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n}}\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.5.2|Speed buffs can no longer be increased with Qi Seasoning. Buff durations from seasoned food/drink are now 50% longer.}}\n\n[[Category:Special items]]\n\n[[de:Qi-Würze]]\n[[es:Condimento Qi]]\n[[fr:Assaisonnement de Qi]]\n[[it:Condimento Qi]]\n[[ja:Qi調味料]]\n[[ko:치의 양념]]\n[[hu:Qi fűszerkeverék]]\n[[pt:Tempero Qi]]\n[[ru:Приправа Ки]]\n[[tr:Qi Çeşnisi]]\n[[zh:齐氏调味料]]"
